== Ōi Shrines List == * {{ill|Ōi Shrine (Mito)|ja|大井神社 (水戸市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōi Shrine (Mito)|qq=}}（[[:en:Ibaraki Prefecture|Ibaraki]] [[Mito, Ibaraki|Mito City]]） - A Shikinaisha (式内社) candidate shrine. The enshrined deity Kashima-no-Mikoto (建借馬命) had the former name Ōfu-no-Omi (意富臣), which later became "Ōi" through phonetic changes. * {{ill|Ōi Shrine (Kasama)|ja|大井神社 (笠間市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōi Shrine (Kasama)|qq=}}（Ibaraki Prefecture [[Kasama, Ibaraki|Kasama City]]） - Shikinaisha candidate shrine. * {{ill|Oi Shrine|ja|大井神社 (島田市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oi Shrine|qq=}}（[[Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka]] [[Shimada, Shizuoka|Shimada City]]） - Kokushi Genzaisha (国史見在社) and Beppyo Shrine (別表神社). Famous for the [[Shimada Obi Festival|Shimada no Obi Matsuri]]. There are several other shrines with the same name along the [[Ōi River (Shizuoka)|Ōi River]] basin. * {{ill|Ōi Shrine (Nagoya)|ja|大井神社 (名古屋市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōi Shrine (Nagoya)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}（[[:en:Aichi Prefecture|Aichi]] [[Nagoya|Nagoya City]]） * {{ill|Ōi Shrine (Aisai)|ja|大井神社 (愛西市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōi Shrine (Aisai)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}（Aichi Prefecture [[:en:Aisai, Aichi|Aisai City]]） * {{ill|Ōi Shrine (Kitagata)|ja|大井神社 (北方町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōi Shrine (Kitagata)|qq=}}（[[:en:Gifu Prefecture|Gifu]] [[Kitagata, Gifu|Kitagata Town]] [[Motosu District, Gifu|Motosu District]]） * {{ill|Ōi Shrine (Kyoto)|ja|大井神社 (京都市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōi Shrine (Kyoto)|qq=}}（[[Kyoto Prefecture|Kyoto]] [[Kyoto|Kyoto City]] [[Ukyō-ku, Kyoto|Ukyō Ward]]） - Shikinaisha candidate shrine. Named after the [[Ōigawa (Kyoto)|Ōi River (Kyoto)]]. * {{ill|Ōi Shrine (Kameoka)|ja|大井神社 (亀岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōi Shrine (Kameoka)|qq=}}（Kyoto Prefecture [[Kameoka, Kyoto|Kameoka City]]） - Shikinaisha. ==意非神社== * {{ill|Oi Shrine (Tottori)|ja|意非神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oi Shrine (Tottori)|qq=}}
